adjectives.description: proteinaceous (comparative more proteinaceous, superlative most proteinaceous)

entries.meaning: Of, pertaining to, or consisting of protein
examples: A few types of molecules get sensed by receptors on the tongue. Protons coming off of acids ping receptors for "sour." Sugars get received as "sweet." Bitter, salty, and the proteinaceous flavor umami all set off their own neural cascades.
